// import React from 'react'; import './App.css'; import React, { Component } from 'react'; import Card from './Components/Card.jsx'; import { isDeclareTypeAlias } from '@babel/types'; class About extends Component { render() { return (

Education

  • University of Waterloo
    • Bachelor of Computer Science
    • John and Karen Wetmore Scholarship
    • President's Scholarship of Distinction
  • Westmount Secondary
    • Senior Girls Waterpolo
    • Senior Girls Basketball
    • Wind Orchestra, Flute

Awards

  • Senior Girls Basketball Championship
    2016-2017 HWDSB Division II
  • Excellence in Math
    Graduation award presented by Westmount Secondary
    100% MCV4U, 99% MHF4U, 98% MDM4U
  • Senior Computer Science Award
    Earned 99% in ICS4U and 98% in ICS3U
  • Cayley Honour Roll
    Top 10% of all contest participants

Interests

  • Snowboarding 🏂
    Started in 2017, now my favourite thing in the world
  • Strength Training 🏋
    PR Bench: 125lb (96% body weight)
  • Board Games 🎲
    Pandemic, Splendor, Risk, Clue, Monopoly
  • Basketball 🏀
    Best team sport to be invented
  • Investing 📈
    Glorified gambling
  • Pets 🐹
    Specifically hamsters
); } } export default About;
